708031f-a.text:
Third Avenue (foreground), west side, at E. 29th Street (left) as viewed from a roof top on the easterly side of the Avenue and showing the Metropolitan and the New York Life Insurance Company's Buildings across the roof of St. Stephens R.C. Church. The latter is entered from E. 28th Street and extends thru the block. Loft structures seen are in the Fourth
Avenue vicinity.
April 30, 1930
P.L. Sperr

December 23, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
